- Safety Measures
The safety of everyone involved in the delivery chain is our priority
- Delivery executives are trained in the best hygiene protocol and have been equipped with masks, gloves & sanitizers
- Delivery executives are frequently tested to avoid any possible Covid infection and will be vaccinated as soon as vaccines re available in Maharashtra
- Delivery boxes are sanitized after each delivery completion 
- All deliveries are non-contact deliveries, unless requested otherwise by our customers
- A Best Safety Standards collection, which includes restaurants that conduct mandatory temperature checks, frequently sanitize their kitchens and ensure daily changes of gloves & masks

